- Yeah.

28:45.515 --> 28:46.767
Would you invite me back?

28:46.767 --> 28:49.394
- Oh, November 23rd.
[laughter]

28:49.394 --> 28:51.188
[cheers and applause]
Listen, what a pleasure.

28:51.188 --> 28:53.565
May I just say,
good luck to you.

28:53.565 --> 28:55.651
God be with you.
